      • restrict

        default IMessageHandler restrict​(@NotNull
                                 MessageKind atLeastOfKind)
        Parameters:
        atLeastOfKind - use MessageKind.ERROR to filter out warnings and info, use MessageKind.WARNING to show errors and warnings only. Use of MessageKind.INFORMATION makes no sense and effectively a no-op.
